    "source_code": "def halve(n):\n    if n <= 1:\n        return 0\n    result = halve(n - 2)\n    return 1 + result\n\ndef main():\n    result1 = halve(4)\n    result2 = halve(7)\n    print(result1)\n    print(result2)\n\nmain()"
